MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 908986980}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 89932b723f1eb074b9ef7a188418672b, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::Dialogue3
  ScavengerLines:
  - Ahhhh that's much better! I can feel the oil circulating in my mobility components!
  - W...wait a minute! You're one of THEM!
  - Bots like YOU are the reason why bots like ME end up stuck under filthy scrap
    heaps!
  - ...
  - Look, I can tell that you don't want to be here...and this scrapyard isn't big
    enough for the both of us... I may have a way to help you escape.
  - 'But help doesn''t come for free around here... '
  - I lost my arm somwhere over by the old Windmill. If you find it and bring it
    to me, I will tell you how to escape.
  - Head to the north east path. Meet me inside the shuttle once you have my arm.
    I will tell you how to escape.
  DialogueIndex: 0
  DialogueUi3: {fileID: 908986980}
  scavmove: {fileID: 1144254465}
  dialogueui: {fileID: 908986983}
  PlayerMove: {fileID: 3828621389755395}
  PlayerShoot: {fileID: 3828621389755394}
